plot: They find a lost dog at Doodlebop Central who they name Strudle Doodle after he eats Rooney's dessert. They become attached to him but decide to try to find his owner. A mother and daughter show up at the theater looking for their "Clyde".
title: "The Doodlebops" Strudle Doodle
